event.title: the 1980s and 1990s, Woodville and its surrounds became

data.event: During the 1980s and 1990s, Woodville and its surrounds became home to many Vietnamese refugees from the Vietnam War.
Decline set in in the 1980s upon the closure of the Cheltenham plant of General Motors Holden.
